de.ovgu.featureide.core.fstmodel

Class FSTModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ovgu.featureide.core.fstmodel.FSTModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FSTModelForPP

    public class FSTModel
extends java.lang.Object
    The FSTModel represents the projects structure.
    FSTClasses and FSTFeatures can have a shared FSTRole.
    For a visualization of the FSTModels structure see lib/FSTModel.jpg.
    Author:
    Jens Meinicke
